WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 37=

00:02:10.690 --> 00:02:11.530 line:80%
- Mr. Mu.
- Mr. Mu.

00:02:13.210 --> 00:02:14.090 line:80%
Most followers

00:02:14.090 --> 00:02:15.900 line:80%
are helping Qingque Sect
heal the wounded

00:02:15.900 --> 00:02:16.740 line:80%
and clean up the mess.

00:02:17.300 --> 00:02:18.690 line:80%
The rest await your orders.

00:02:19.370 --> 00:02:20.780 line:80%
My time is running out.

00:02:20.780 --> 00:02:21.620 line:80%
- Mr. Mu.
- Mr. Mu.

00:02:21.620 --> 00:02:22.970 line:80%
No need to say more.

00:02:23.690 --> 00:02:24.780 line:80%
From now on,

00:02:26.930 --> 00:02:29.020 line:80%
you two will jointly manage the Li Sect.

00:02:30.340 --> 00:02:31.180 line:80%
Gradually open trade

00:02:32.530 --> 00:02:34.410 line:80%
with the Six Sects.

00:02:34.860 --> 00:02:36.060 line:80%
Coexist in harmony.

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:46.530 line:80%
All plans are

00:02:46.530 --> 00:02:47.530 line:80%
in this handbook.

00:02:48.180 --> 00:02:49.090 line:80%
After I'm gone,

00:02:49.650 --> 00:02:51.460 line:80%
if you clash with the Six Sects,

00:02:53.460 --> 00:02:54.780 line:80%
you can go to Song Yuzhi

00:02:55.300 --> 00:02:56.370 line:80%
to negotiate a solution.

00:03:04.810 --> 00:03:05.650 line:80%
Yes.

00:03:09.180 --> 00:03:10.460 line:80%
For Zhao's future,

00:03:13.810 --> 00:03:16.060 line:80%
I only wish her peace and smoothness.

00:03:19.900 --> 00:03:20.780 line:80%
If

00:03:23.140 --> 00:03:24.740 line:80%
she finds a good person,

00:03:28.650 --> 00:03:30.180 line:80%
please be sure to

00:03:31.410 --> 00:03:32.530 line:80%
protect her.

00:03:34.090 --> 00:03:34.930 line:80%
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:03:36.900 --> 00:03:37.740 line:80%
Go.

00:04:29.340 --> 00:04:30.180 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:31.140 --> 00:04:33.780 line:80%
the first half of my life was hard.

00:04:34.940 --> 00:04:35.940 line:80%
Surviving

00:04:36.730 --> 00:04:38.410 line:80%
was my only wish.

00:04:39.820 --> 00:04:41.290 line:80%
Not until I met you

00:04:43.210 --> 00:04:45.730 line:80%
did I know the meaning of living.

00:04:49.820 --> 00:04:52.500 line:80%
Like candlelight piercing the darkness.

00:04:55.380 --> 00:04:57.610 line:80%
Like the fragrant curling cooking smoke.

00:04:59.090 --> 00:05:00.290 line:80%
I'm sorry, Zhao.

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:02.220 line:80%
I broke my promise.

00:05:04.700 --> 00:05:06.850 line:80%
I still used the Disintegration.

00:05:15.090 --> 00:05:15.930 line:80%
Zhao.

00:05:17.380 --> 00:05:18.380 line:80%
We made a pact.

00:05:21.340 --> 00:05:22.580 line:80%
After I die,

00:05:23.580 --> 00:05:25.900 line:80%
bury my ashes under
that tri-colored peach blossoms tree

00:05:25.900 --> 00:05:27.610 line:80%
in Luoying Valley.

00:05:29.170 --> 00:05:30.940 line:80%
That way, whether I become a breeze

00:05:33.050 --> 00:05:34.020 line:80%
or a grain of sand,

00:05:36.530 --> 00:05:38.340 line:80%
I'll always stay by your side.

00:05:40.900 --> 00:05:42.020 line:80%
If one day,

00:05:42.970 --> 00:05:44.460 line:80%
you find another good match,

00:05:46.580 --> 00:05:48.530 line:80%
I'll be truly happy for you.

00:05:54.940 --> 00:05:56.410 line:80%
You won't die.

00:05:57.530 --> 00:05:58.850 line:80%
And I'll never find

00:05:59.610 --> 00:06:01.050 line:80%
another good match.

00:06:05.700 --> 00:06:06.540 line:80%
Zhao,

00:06:09.020 --> 00:06:10.530 line:80%
I owe you so much

00:06:11.290 --> 00:06:12.730 line:80%
in this life.

00:06:15.730 --> 00:06:17.340 line:80%
I hope you don't blame me.

00:06:18.730 --> 00:06:20.170 line:80%
Don't resent me.

00:06:23.140 --> 00:06:24.460 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:06:25.900 --> 00:06:27.650 line:80%
In this life,

00:06:29.290 --> 00:06:30.940 line:80%
you're the only one I ever loved.

00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:37.900 line:80%
Every time I think of
the seven Python Whips you endured.

00:06:40.290 --> 00:06:41.130 line:80%
I know

00:06:43.090 --> 00:06:44.650 line:80%
you took that punishment

00:06:45.580 --> 00:06:48.210 line:80%
to cut ties with me for good.

00:06:49.820 --> 00:06:51.140 line:80%
But in my heart,

00:06:51.940 --> 00:06:52.850 line:80%
it's the opposite.

00:06:53.820 --> 00:06:55.020 line:80%
In my midnight dreams,

00:06:58.290 --> 00:07:00.700 line:80%
I see you covered in blood.

00:07:03.020 --> 00:07:04.210 line:80%
And at that moment,

00:07:06.610 --> 00:07:08.020 line:80%
I know I have no way to escape.

00:07:13.170 --> 00:07:14.650 line:80%
Then don't escape.

00:07:16.780 --> 00:07:18.900 line:80%
We'll never be apart again.

00:07:45.340 --> 00:07:46.780 line:80%
If I have time

00:07:49.210 --> 00:07:51.020 line:80%
to ride the Golden Peng with you

00:07:52.780 --> 00:07:54.210 line:80%
and revisit the Hanhai Mountains,

00:07:56.380 --> 00:07:57.220 line:80%
how nice that would be.

00:07:59.380 --> 00:08:00.220 line:80%
Okay.

00:08:02.460 --> 00:08:03.820 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:08:24.140 --> 00:08:25.970 line:80%
Zhao, will you go back to
Carefree Chamber with me?

00:08:29.580 --> 00:08:30.530 line:80%
I will.

00:08:32.570 --> 00:08:34.530 line:80%
I'll stay with you

00:08:34.530 --> 00:08:36.020 line:80%
as long as you want.

00:08:47.780 --> 00:08:52.820 line:80%
♪If we never met♪

00:08:54.210 --> 00:08:57.700 line:80%
♪Would there be no longing♪

00:08:57.710 --> 00:08:58.550 line:80%
Zhao.

00:09:00.730 --> 00:09:02.780 line:80%
♪In that fleeting moment♪

00:09:03.450 --> 00:09:05.050 line:80%
You'll look beautiful

00:09:08.050 --> 00:09:09.410 line:80%
in a wedding dress.

00:09:09.890 --> 00:09:13.640 line:80%
♪Countless times♪

00:09:14.290 --> 00:09:15.650 line:80%
When you get better,

00:09:18.500 --> 00:09:19.810 line:80%
we'll get married.

00:09:20.350 --> 00:09:22.710 line:80%
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

00:09:22.710 --> 00:09:26.920 line:80%
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

00:09:27.420 --> 00:09:29.320 line:80%
♪Holding you and me♪

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:33.730 line:80%
♪Life spreads without boundary♪

00:09:34.030 --> 00:09:36.710 line:80%
♪After parting♪

00:09:37.210 --> 00:09:39.490 line:80%
♪Before death♪

00:09:40.650 --> 00:09:45.170 line:80%
♪We meet no more♪

00:10:12.100 --> 00:10:17.010 line:80%
♪If we never met♪

00:10:17.920 --> 00:10:18.850 line:80%
Zhao.

00:10:18.850 --> 00:10:23.630 line:80%
♪Life is full of hardships♪

00:10:25.140 --> 00:10:27.280 line:80%
♪In dreams♪

00:10:28.010 --> 00:10:31.010 line:80%
♪I become a sleeping lotus♪

00:10:31.630 --> 00:10:33.850 line:80%
♪Before awakening♪

00:10:34.110 --> 00:10:37.460 line:80%
♪I have already lost sleep♪

00:10:38.070 --> 00:10:40.560 line:80%
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:43.550 line:80%
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

00:10:43.570 --> 00:10:45.110 line:80%
Zhao!

00:10:46.380 --> 00:10:48.860 line:80%
Zhao!

00:10:51.780 --> 00:10:54.610 line:80%
♪After this life♪

00:10:56.450 --> 00:10:57.980 line:80%
Zhao!

00:10:58.490 --> 00:11:03.130 line:80%
♪We meet no more♪

00:11:03.290 --> 00:11:06.530 line:80%
Zhao!

00:11:10.380 --> 00:11:11.900 line:80%
Go back and bury your father properly.

00:11:12.290 --> 00:11:14.220 line:80%
From now on,
this manor will depend on you.

00:11:14.900 --> 00:11:16.380 line:80%
If you ever run into trouble,

00:11:16.690 --> 00:11:17.530 line:80%
Luoying Valley

00:11:17.780 --> 00:11:19.100 line:80%
will surely help.

00:11:19.690 --> 00:11:20.740 line:80%
Thank you, Uncle Cai.

00:11:22.450 --> 00:11:23.650 line:80%
About Zhao's matter...

00:11:23.650 --> 00:11:25.380 line:80%
Let's not mention the past.

00:11:25.740 --> 00:11:28.170 line:80%
It's good you've each found

00:11:28.980 --> 00:11:29.820 line:80%
your own happiness.

00:11:30.900 --> 00:11:32.450 line:80%
Siqi Sect has been troubled
for a long time.

00:11:32.900 --> 00:11:34.650 line:80%
Those old folks inside
aren't easy to deal with.

00:11:35.170 --> 00:11:36.620 line:80%
If you can't handle it alone,

00:11:37.780 --> 00:11:38.780 line:80%
don't push yourself.

00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:41.380 line:80%
Come find me at Luoying Valley anytime.

00:11:43.450 --> 00:11:44.620 line:80%
When it comes to arguing,

00:11:45.050 --> 00:11:46.980 line:80%
I have never lost.

00:11:47.450 --> 00:11:49.570 line:80%
Don't worry, Aunt. I won't overdo it.

00:11:50.740 --> 00:11:53.170 line:80%
If it can't be done in a day,
I'll wait a year.

00:11:53.170 --> 00:11:56.170 line:80%
If a year won't do, I'll wait ten.

00:11:56.170 --> 00:11:57.450 line:80%
I have patience.

00:11:57.450 --> 00:11:59.330 line:80%
I'll eventually clean up
Siqi Sect thoroughly.

00:11:59.330 --> 00:12:01.220 line:80%
Give the martial arts world
an explanation.

00:12:03.500 --> 00:12:04.980 line:80%
You want to take a third wife?

00:12:06.780 --> 00:12:08.290 line:80%
Clean up your mind.

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:10.690 line:80%
There's pure admiration
between men and women too.

00:12:12.020 --> 00:12:13.620 line:80%
Your thoughts are so dirty.

00:12:13.620 --> 00:12:15.380 line:80%
Be careful, I'll tell Xing.

00:12:17.050 --> 00:12:17.890 line:80%
Let's go.

00:12:18.690 --> 00:12:19.930 line:80%
It's about time we head back.

00:12:22.930 --> 00:12:23.770 line:80%
Yeah.

00:12:24.170 --> 00:12:25.620 line:80%
It's about time we head back.

00:15:19.530 --> 00:15:20.370 line:80%
Zhao.

00:15:38.690 --> 00:15:40.500 line:80%
It's like heaven never shuts all doors.

00:15:41.450 --> 00:15:42.650 line:80%
In the end, he made a desperate move.

00:15:43.450 --> 00:15:45.050 line:80%
He used the Disintegration to

00:15:45.050 --> 00:15:46.290 line:80%
force his inner power to surge.

00:15:47.330 --> 00:15:49.650 line:80%
But he'd already passed
all his inner power to you.

00:15:50.020 --> 00:15:51.020 line:80%
Only the Suzi Fragrance poison

00:15:51.530 --> 00:15:52.930 line:80%
remained in his meridians.

00:15:54.980 --> 00:15:56.020 line:80%
That evil technique

00:15:56.690 --> 00:15:58.500 line:80%
actually forced out all the poison.

00:17:39.420 --> 00:17:40.610 line:80%
Why go to such great lengths to

00:17:41.090 --> 00:17:42.220 line:80%
bring Qi Yunke's remains

00:17:42.810 --> 00:17:44.290 line:80%
from the Sinner's Stone Forest?

00:17:45.370 --> 00:17:46.500 line:80%
With Master as company,

00:17:47.460 --> 00:17:49.570 line:80%
I think aunt will be happy.

00:17:49.940 --> 00:17:52.220 line:80%
Qi Yunke did so many bad things
in his life.

00:17:53.570 --> 00:17:55.090 line:80%
Do you think your aunt will be happy?

00:17:57.780 --> 00:17:59.810 line:80%
After my aunt came back
seriously injured,

00:17:59.810 --> 00:18:00.740 line:80%
she refused medicine and

00:18:01.290 --> 00:18:02.220 line:80%
planned to die.

00:18:03.130 --> 00:18:05.460 line:80%
She was afraid
I'd be bullied in the future.

00:18:05.460 --> 00:18:06.660 line:80%
So she forced herself to

00:18:07.780 --> 00:18:09.570 line:80%
teach me martial arts and formations.

00:18:09.940 --> 00:18:11.420 line:80%
And how to behave.

00:18:12.290 --> 00:18:13.130 line:80%
That's how

00:18:13.290 --> 00:18:14.700 line:80%
she got through each day.

00:18:15.420 --> 00:18:17.090 line:80%
She managed to hold on
for over ten years.

00:18:17.940 --> 00:18:19.050 line:80%
During those years,

00:18:19.460 --> 00:18:20.420 line:80%
only master

00:18:21.180 --> 00:18:22.780 line:80%
came to heal aunt every year

00:18:23.780 --> 00:18:24.810 line:80%
and chatted with her.

00:18:25.460 --> 00:18:26.980 line:80%
Whenever she was with master,

00:18:27.330 --> 00:18:28.530 line:80%
my aunt always had a smile.

00:18:29.290 --> 00:18:30.130 line:80%
So

00:18:30.850 --> 00:18:32.460 line:80%
master must be

00:18:33.890 --> 00:18:35.570 line:80%
the most important person to aunt.

00:18:38.020 --> 00:18:39.370 line:80%
Compared to seeking revenge,

00:18:41.180 --> 00:18:42.090 line:80%
this kind of companionship

00:18:42.610 --> 00:18:43.700 line:80%
is the most precious.

00:18:49.500 --> 00:18:50.340 line:80%
This...

00:18:51.460 --> 00:18:52.660 line:80%
belongs to Mu Zhengyang.

00:18:54.130 --> 00:18:55.330 line:80%
Or rather

00:18:55.330 --> 00:18:56.980 line:80%
it's a gift from Ms. Cai
to Mu Zhengyang.

00:18:59.530 --> 00:19:00.370 line:80%
I think

00:19:00.660 --> 00:19:01.700 line:80%
leaving it here

00:19:02.530 --> 00:19:03.890 line:80%
is the best choice.

00:19:05.330 --> 00:19:06.170 line:80%
That's good.

00:19:06.530 --> 00:19:07.460 line:80%
This way,

00:19:07.460 --> 00:19:09.740 line:80%
they can chat and recall the past.

00:19:15.420 --> 00:19:16.420 line:80%
Aunt,

00:19:16.420 --> 00:19:17.740 line:80%
you've stayed in solitude for so long.

00:19:18.570 --> 00:19:20.020 line:80%
It's time for a bit of
warmth and company.

00:19:21.130 --> 00:19:22.500 line:80%
We were once travelers,

00:19:23.050 --> 00:19:24.420 line:80%
drowning in wine-induced cheer.

00:19:24.890 --> 00:19:26.090 line:80%
Since we parted like floating clouds,

00:19:26.350 --> 00:19:27.660 line:80%
ten years have drifted away.

00:19:28.460 --> 00:19:29.330 line:80%
However brilliant

00:19:29.330 --> 00:19:31.050 line:80%
one may be,

00:19:32.330 --> 00:19:34.940 line:80%
however astonishing one's feats

00:19:34.940 --> 00:19:35.780 line:80%
and passions once were,

00:19:36.180 --> 00:19:37.050 line:80%
in the end,

00:19:38.090 --> 00:19:39.180 line:80%
all return

00:19:40.810 --> 00:19:41.650 line:80%
to dust.

00:19:42.570 --> 00:19:43.660 line:80%
Living in this world,

00:19:44.130 --> 00:19:45.090 line:80%
I often wonder

00:19:45.850 --> 00:19:47.500 line:80%
what truly matters most.

00:19:47.810 --> 00:19:48.780 line:80%
Aunt once said

00:19:49.660 --> 00:19:50.850 line:80%
that to live in this world,

00:19:51.940 --> 00:19:52.810 line:80%
what matters most

00:19:53.420 --> 00:19:54.980 line:80%
is to be sensible and joyful each day,

00:19:56.050 --> 00:19:57.890 line:80%
with no shame when looking up or down.

00:19:58.980 --> 00:20:00.050 line:80%
The Yin clan may one day fall.

00:20:00.740 --> 00:20:01.940 line:80%
The Nie clan may vanish too.

00:20:02.570 --> 00:20:03.410 line:80%
We

00:20:04.780 --> 00:20:05.810 line:80%
will never perish.

00:20:09.500 --> 00:20:10.340 line:80%
We

00:20:11.420 --> 00:20:12.610 line:80%
will never perish.

00:20:16.740 --> 00:20:18.020 line:80%
(Breeze)

00:20:34.220 --> 00:20:35.370 line:80%
Aunt!

00:20:35.370 --> 00:20:36.420 line:80%
Master.

00:20:36.420 --> 00:20:37.740 line:80%
This is Breeze.

00:20:37.740 --> 00:20:39.940 line:80%
Uncle Lei asked me to bring it to you.

00:20:39.940 --> 00:20:41.220 line:80%
If you know from the other side,

00:20:42.370 --> 00:20:43.940 line:80%
now we can share a drink again.

00:21:54.220 --> 00:21:58.900 line:80%
(Sunshine Blade Manual)

00:22:09.300 --> 00:22:11.620 line:80%
(Sunshine Blade Manual)

00:22:19.610 --> 00:22:20.450 line:80%
This way, please.

00:22:23.500 --> 00:22:24.940 line:80%
- You're so thoughtful.
- Please.

00:22:24.940 --> 00:22:26.220 line:80%
Here, hand that to me.

00:22:31.170 --> 00:22:32.010 line:80%
Hang it higher.

00:22:34.570 --> 00:22:35.610 line:80%
Elder Yan thinks

00:22:35.980 --> 00:22:37.500 line:80%
the Six Sects just went through turmoil,

00:22:37.940 --> 00:22:39.570 line:80%
so it's a time of transition.

00:22:40.530 --> 00:22:42.460 line:80%
He still wants to persuade
Young Master to go back

00:22:42.460 --> 00:22:44.570 line:80%
to complete Li Sect's great cause
of unifying the Six Sects.

00:22:44.570 --> 00:22:45.410 line:80%
Well now,

00:22:45.870 --> 00:22:47.130 line:80%
Young Master is married just like that.

00:22:48.530 --> 00:22:49.370 line:80%
No.

00:22:49.570 --> 00:22:52.050 line:80%
He's marrying into
this vibrant Luoying Valley.

00:22:54.180 --> 00:22:56.980 line:80%
Young Master!

00:22:56.980 --> 00:22:58.740 line:80%
Look how hopeless you are.

00:23:00.180 --> 00:23:01.020 line:80%
Xing.

00:23:01.700 --> 00:23:03.050 line:80%
Young Master's marriage

00:23:03.050 --> 00:23:04.050 line:80%
is a happy event.

00:23:04.610 --> 00:23:05.610 line:80%
Besides,

00:23:06.090 --> 00:23:08.850 line:80%
none of the new generation of
the Six Sects are easy to deal with.

00:23:08.850 --> 00:23:10.940 line:80%
Like Lord of Siqi Sect, Yang Xiaolan.

00:23:11.220 --> 00:23:13.460 line:80%
Rumor has it she's mastered
the Sunshine Blade Technique.

00:23:13.810 --> 00:23:15.850 line:80%
And Song Yuzhi,
the new Lord of the Qingque Sect.

00:23:16.290 --> 00:23:18.330 line:80%
He reorganized the sect
in just a few months.

00:23:19.530 --> 00:23:21.460 line:80%
If we really fight the Six Sects again

00:23:21.460 --> 00:23:22.740 line:80%
as Elder Yan said,

00:23:22.740 --> 00:23:23.850 line:80%
can we still live in peace?

00:23:24.290 --> 00:23:25.130 line:80%
Yes.

00:23:25.420 --> 00:23:26.260 line:80%
Of course we can.

00:23:26.560 --> 00:23:27.420 line:80%
Dear.

00:23:27.420 --> 00:23:28.810 line:80%
Don't carry such heavy things.

00:23:30.810 --> 00:23:31.650 line:80%
Let me do it.

00:23:33.850 --> 00:23:34.700 line:80%
Alright, coming.

00:23:36.420 --> 00:23:38.290 line:80%
Welcome, Master Shangguan.

00:23:39.570 --> 00:23:40.410 line:80%
My flowers!

00:23:43.010 --> 00:23:43.850 line:80%
You stepped on them.

00:23:43.850 --> 00:23:44.690 line:80%
I...

00:23:47.330 --> 00:23:48.460 line:80%
Where to put Young Master's dowry?

00:23:48.940 --> 00:23:49.780 line:80%
Follow me.

00:23:51.570 --> 00:23:52.410 line:80%
Put it here.

00:23:57.320 --> 00:23:58.300 line:80%
Come on, let's have some tea.

00:24:02.530 --> 00:24:03.370 line:80%
Smiley.

00:24:04.660 --> 00:24:05.530 line:80%
I can't smile.

00:24:08.570 --> 00:24:09.530 line:80%
In three days,

00:24:09.940 --> 00:24:11.330 line:80%
Young Master
will be part of the Cai clan.

00:24:18.290 --> 00:24:19.370 line:80%
So sweet!

00:24:20.850 --> 00:24:21.690 line:80%
Tastes good.

00:24:21.940 --> 00:24:24.130 line:80%
Young Master ordered these
at the fruit shop east of town.

00:24:24.130 --> 00:24:25.370 line:80%
Heard it's improved with licoric.

00:24:25.370 --> 00:24:26.370 line:80%
Too many won't cause internal heat.

00:24:26.370 --> 00:24:27.460 line:80%
I'll take a few jin back

00:24:27.460 --> 00:24:29.180 line:80%
as gifts for the brothers
of Qinglong Altar.

00:24:29.180 --> 00:24:30.330 line:80%
I'll buy a few jin for my wives.

00:24:30.780 --> 00:24:32.020 line:80%
To keep them from being bored

00:24:32.420 --> 00:24:33.260 line:80%
and nagging me every day.

00:24:34.220 --> 00:24:35.420 line:80%
I'm different from you.

00:24:36.220 --> 00:24:38.020 line:80%
I love watching our Xing nag.

00:24:59.330 --> 00:25:01.020 line:80%
This dress style is nice.

00:25:01.570 --> 00:25:03.180 line:80%
But the craftsmanship's a bit rough.

00:25:03.660 --> 00:25:04.740 line:80%
(Tea House)
Needs reworking.

00:25:04.740 --> 00:25:06.020 line:80%
(Inn; Spicy Skewer Shop)

00:25:09.500 --> 00:25:10.370 line:80%
This wax...

00:25:10.370 --> 00:25:11.610 line:80%
Too much of it will produce heavy smoke.

00:25:11.980 --> 00:25:14.050 line:80%
Later, I'll have Shangguan
go back to the Hanhai Mountains

00:25:14.420 --> 00:25:16.220 line:80%
to get some merman wax
from the treasury.

00:25:16.660 --> 00:25:17.500 line:80%
It burns longer

00:25:17.710 --> 00:25:18.650 line:80%
and has a special fragrance.

00:25:19.850 --> 00:25:20.980 line:80%
We can ride the Golden Peng back.

00:25:20.980 --> 00:25:22.220 line:80%
Just in time for the auspicious day.

00:25:24.040 --> 00:25:26.020 line:80%
(Guest: Li Sect, You Guanyue and Xing)
Six Sects and Li Sect

00:25:26.020 --> 00:25:27.180 line:80%
have been peaceful now,

00:25:27.700 --> 00:25:29.220 line:80%
but there are still some old grievances.

00:25:30.130 --> 00:25:31.460 line:80%
We still need to separate their seats

00:25:32.050 --> 00:25:32.890 line:80%
at the banquet.

00:25:36.020 --> 00:25:36.860 line:80%
Zhao,

00:25:41.810 --> 00:25:42.650 line:80%
what are you drawing?

00:25:42.980 --> 00:25:44.290 line:80%
Do you think the clothing shop

00:25:44.290 --> 00:25:45.780 line:80%
should be in front of the shoe shop?

00:25:46.220 --> 00:25:47.060 line:80%
Or behind?

00:25:47.660 --> 00:25:48.520 line:80%
Should the candy shop

00:25:48.520 --> 00:25:50.090 line:80%
be next to the spicy skewer shop?

00:25:50.460 --> 00:25:52.020 line:80%
You're wasting such good time

00:25:52.700 --> 00:25:54.370 line:80%
on this?

00:25:54.850 --> 00:25:55.700 line:80%
Yeah,

00:25:55.700 --> 00:25:57.050 line:80%
it's such a rare chance.

00:25:57.810 --> 00:25:58.650 line:80%
Think about it.

00:25:58.890 --> 00:25:59.740 line:80%
When the time comes,

00:25:59.740 --> 00:26:01.500 line:80%
people from the Six Sects
and Li Sect will all come.

00:26:01.500 --> 00:26:02.740 line:80%
The threshold of Luoying Valley

00:26:02.740 --> 00:26:03.890 line:80%
will be worn out.

00:26:03.890 --> 00:26:05.700 line:80%
All the storytellers across the Jianghu

00:26:05.700 --> 00:26:06.890 line:80%
must shout a line or two.

00:26:07.500 --> 00:26:08.340 line:80%
And what does that mean?

00:26:09.740 --> 00:26:10.980 line:80%
That's our chance.

00:26:11.570 --> 00:26:13.850 line:80%
Whether Xingjia and I
can grow our business

00:26:13.850 --> 00:26:15.220 line:80%
depends on this.

00:26:15.220 --> 00:26:16.460 line:80%
Since Ms. Cai

00:26:16.460 --> 00:26:18.220 line:80%
cares only about doing business

00:26:18.220 --> 00:26:19.890 line:80%
and nothing about marriage,

00:26:20.420 --> 00:26:21.370 line:80%
(Guest)
Then this wedding

00:26:21.370 --> 00:26:22.210 line:80%
doesn't need to happen.

