a lifetime of harmony!

00:27:15.660 --> 00:27:16.810 line:80%
Welcome, welcome!

00:27:16.810 --> 00:27:17.700 line:80%
Long time no see.

00:27:18.180 --> 00:27:19.740 line:80%
Here, here are the gifts.

00:27:20.810 --> 00:27:22.780 line:80%
