00:27:23.660 --> 00:27:25.020 line:80%
Gifts from Peiqiong Manor.

00:27:25.020 --> 00:27:26.330 line:80%
A hundred golden silk armors.

00:27:26.330 --> 00:27:27.700 line:80%
A thousand taels of gold.

00:27:27.920 --> 00:27:28.940 line:80%
Just the little gifts from us.

00:27:29.810 --> 00:27:32.810 line:80%
