00:31:10.090 --> 00:31:10.930 line:80%
Shangguan.

00:31:11.130 --> 00:31:12.290 line:80%
Who is this Wan Dazhuang?

00:31:12.850 --> 00:31:13.780 line:80%
Never heard of him before.

00:31:14.420 --> 00:31:15.330 line:80%
