00:31:23.180 --> 00:31:24.050 line:80%
His name is Wan Dazhuang.

00:31:35.940 --> 00:31:37.570 line:80%
Eternal unity!

00:31:40.980 --> 00:31:41.980 line:80%
As you wish,

00:31:42.890 --> 00:31:44.370 line:80%
